title: 175: Don't let these people listen to Mind Pump
description: There are some people who should never listen to Mind Pump. Children are one group that immediately comes to mind but Sal, Adam & Justin can think of a few adults they hope will never hear the show. Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Learn more about Mind Pump at www.mindpumpradio.com
